rows.label: tlk400906_msg0001
rows.name: What? You need something from me?

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0002
rows.name: We want to ask about Black Ash, mo.

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0003
rows.name:
About Black Ash... huh.
Isset told you, didn't he?

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0004
rows.name: That is correct, mo.

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0005
rows.name: That guy...

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0006
rows.name:
Well, it's not like I'm
doing anything wrong, so
I'll tell you straight.

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0007
rows.name: What do you want to know?

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0008
rows.name:
Have you been selling large
quantities of Black Ash somewhere?

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0009
rows.name:
Not a huge amount, but I make regular
deliveries of a few barrels.

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0010
rows.name:
For shielding an ether
furnace, you might not
need that much at once, mo.

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0011
rows.name: I see...

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0012
rows.name: So, where are you delivering it?

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0013
rows.name:
Near the entrance to the
Old Industrial District.

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0014
rows.name:
I just leave it at the
designated spot, so I've
never seen the buyer's face.

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0015
rows.name: That's suspicious...

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0016
rows.name: You think so?

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0017
rows.name:
The pay is good and the
price is fair. I've never
thought it was suspicious.

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0018
rows.name:
If you're making something
outside the city, it's a waste
of effort to haul it inside.

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0019
rows.name:
And it's a pain to arrange
a meeting time, right?

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0020
rows.name: That might be true, but...

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0021
rows.name: When is the next delivery?

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0022
rows.name: In ten days.

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0023
rows.name: Ugh. We have to wait that long?

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0024
rows.name:
Perhaps we should wait and
enjoy the hot springs.

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0025
rows.name: Won't we get all pruny?

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0026
rows.name:
But I just delivered some a
little while ago. If you go
now, it might still be there.

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0027
rows.name: You should have said that first!

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0028
rows.name: Then let's hurry!

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0029
rows.name:
Are the barrels in a
conspicuous place, mo?

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0030
rows.name:
Yeah, I think so.
They're green barrels.

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0031
rows.name:
If you have any more
questions, just ask.
